#: hdrcalibrator.cpp:149 Main.qml:15
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:window"
msgid "HDR Calibration"
msgstr "Kalibracija HDR"

#: Main.qml:187 Main.qml:365
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Next"
msgstr "Naslednji"

#: Main.qml:194 Main.qml:371
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info accessible description of a push button"
msgid "Switches to the next page"
msgstr "Preklopi na naslednjo stran"

#: Main.qml:198 Main.qml:375 Main.qml:475
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Prekliči"

#: Main.qml:201 Main.qml:378 Main.qml:478
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info accessible description of a push button"
msgid "Cancels the calibration process"
msgstr "Prekliče proces kalibracije"

#: Main.qml:210
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"To determine the maximum brightness of the screen, adjust the slider until "
"the logo is barely visible"
msgstr ""
"Če želite določiti največjo svetlost zaslona, ​​​​prilagodite drsnik, dokler "
"logotip ni komaj viden"

#: Main.qml:389
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Configure how bright “100%” on the normal brightness slider should be. Make "
"it as bright as you'd ever use it, as long as the HDR image still looks good "
"and the gradients are smooth.\n"
"To avoid brightness fluctuations, it's recommended to not exceed the "
"display's maximum average brightness of %1cd/m²"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte, kako svetla naj bo \"100%\" na drsniku za normalno "
"svetlost.. Naj bo tako svetla, kot bi jo kdajkoli uporabljali, če je HDR "
"slika še vedno videti dobro in so prelivi gladki.\n"
"Da bi se izognili nihanjem svetlosti, je priporočljivo, da ne presežete "
"največje povprečne svetlosti zaslona, ​​ki znaša %1 cd/m²."

#: Main.qml:391
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Configure how bright “100%” on the normal brightness slider should be. Make "
"it as bright as you'd ever use it, as long as the HDR image still looks good "
"and the gradients are smooth."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte, kako svetla naj bo \"100%\" na drsniku za normalno "
"svetlost.. Naj bo tako svetla, kot bi jo kdajkoli uporabljali, če je HDR "
"slika še vedno videti dobro in so prelivi gladki."

#: Main.qml:438
#, kde-format
msgid "Maximum luminance: %1cd/m²"
msgstr "Maksimalna svetlost: %1cd/m²"

#: Main.qml:459
#, kde-format
msgid "Reference luminance / paper white: %1cd/m²"
msgstr "Referenčna svetlost / papirnato bela: %1cd/m²"

#: Main.qml:470
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:checkbox"
msgid "Assume Windows HDR applications are calibrated for this screen"
msgstr "Predpostavljamo, da so aplikacije Windows HDR kalibrirane za ta zaslon"

#: Main.qml:482
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Done"
msgstr "Narejeno"

#: Main.qml:491
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info accessible description of a push button"
msgid "Finish the calibration process"
msgstr "Končaj proces kalibracije"

#: Main.qml:500
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Many Windows applications come with their own calibration settings, which "
"this system wide configuration conflicts with. If this option is set, their "
"calibration settings will work as expected on this specific display."
msgstr ""
"Številne aplikacije sistema Windows imajo lastne nastavitve kalibracije, s "
"katerimi je ta konfiguracija sistema v navzkrižju. Če je ta možnost "
"nastavljena, bodo njihove nastavitve kalibracije na tem specifičnem zaslonu "
"delovale po pričakovanjih."

